{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/git/github-멀티계정-변경하기---ssh-key/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Dryad","author":"dryad","siteUrl":"https://dryadsoft.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"dryadsoft/dryadsoft.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"jbee"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d81da622-b4b5-5956-b935-fd27eff13a16","excerpt":"목차 1. SSH KEY 생성 2. Gitbub에 ssh public key 등록 3. ssh config 파일 설정 4. ssh 명령어 모음 5. ssh key 설정중 발생한 오류 Github의 여러계정 등록하기 github를 사용하다보면 프로젝트마다 다른 계정을 사용해야 하는 경우가 발생한다.\n이럴때 마다 앞의 포스트에 작성했던 방법으로 계정을 변경하면 매우 귀찮다.\n그리고 설정이 제대로 되어있지 않으면 permission denied 오류가 발생하는 경우가 생긴다. SSH KEY…","html":"<h3 id=\"목차\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AA%A9%EC%B0%A8\" aria-label=\"목차 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a>목차</h3>\n<p><a href=\"#ssh-key-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">1. SSH KEY 생성</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"#gitbub%EC%97%90-ssh-public-key-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D\">2. Gitbub에 ssh public key 등록</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"#ssh-config-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">3. ssh config 파일 설정</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"#ssh-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%EC%96%B4-%EB%AA%A8%EC%9D%8C\">4. ssh 명령어 모음</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"#ssh-key-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%EC%A4%91-%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D%ED%95%9C-%EC%98%A4%EB%A5%98\">5. ssh key 설정중 발생한 오류</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"github의-여러계정-등록하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#github%EC%9D%98-%EC%97%AC%EB%9F%AC%EA%B3%84%EC%A0%95-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"github의 여러계정 등록하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a>Github의 여러계정 등록하기</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>github를 사용하다보면 프로젝트마다 다른 계정을 사용해야 하는 경우가 발생한다.\n이럴때 마다 앞의 <a href=\"https://dryadsoft.github.io/#/posts/git/6\">포스트</a>에 작성했던 방법으로 계정을 변경하면 매우 귀찮다.\n그리고 설정이 제대로 되어있지 않으면 <strong>permission denied</strong> 오류가 발생하는 경우가 생긴다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"div-idssh-key-생성ssh-key-생성div\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#div-idssh-key-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1ssh-key-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1div\" aria-label=\"div idssh key 생성ssh key 생성div permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a><div id=\"ssh-key-생성\">SSH KEY 생성</div></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://help.github.com/en/github/authenticating-to-github/generating-a-new-ssh-key-and-adding-it-to-the-ssh-agent\">GitHub Help</a> 페이지에 나와있는 설명대로 <strong>SSH</strong> KEY를 생성한다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>git bash를 연다.</li>\n<li>ssh key를 생성할 github의 이메일 계정을 입력 후 아래 명령어를 실행한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">    <span class=\"token operator\">></span> ssh-keygen -t rsa -b <span class=\"token number\">4096</span> -C <span class=\"token string\">\"your_email@example.com\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>git bash에 아래 문구가 나오면 key가 생성될 위치를 지정해준다.</li>\n<li>지정하지 않고 엔터키를 누르면 기본경로에 저장 된다.</li>\n<li>여러계정을 등록할 경우 같은경로에 같은이름으로 등록되면 안되기때문에 경로를 변경해준다.</li>\n<li>경로변경시 해당 경로는 반드시 존재하여야한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&gt; Enter a file in which to save the key (/c/Users/you/.ssh/id_rsa):[Press enter]</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>ssh-add 명령어로 key를 등록한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">    <span class=\"token operator\">></span> ssh-add ~/.ssh/id_rsa   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"생성된 id_rsa 키\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>위 방법으로 하면 Windows 10 에서 아래 오류가 발생한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">    <span class=\"token operator\">></span> Could not <span class=\"token function\">open</span> a connection to your authentication agent.</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>아래 명령어로 ssh-agent를 background로 실행시키고 다시 ssh-add명령어를 사용하면 오류가 발생하지 않는다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">    <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">eval</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>ssh-agent -s<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\n    Agent pid <span class=\"token number\">2144</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">></span> ssh-add ~/.ssh/id_rsa   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"생성된 id_rsa 키\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>ssh-add가 정상적으로 등록되었는지 조회한다..</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">    <span class=\"token operator\">></span> ssh-add -l\n    <span class=\"token number\">4096</span> SHA256:aCB<span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>.UT your@email.com <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>RSA<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"div-idgitbub에-ssh-public-key-등록gitbub에-ssh-public-key-등록div\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#div-idgitbub%EC%97%90-ssh-public-key-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9Dgitbub%EC%97%90-ssh-public-key-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9Ddiv\" aria-label=\"div idgitbub에 ssh public key 등록gitbub에 ssh public key 등록div permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a><div id=\"gitbub에-ssh-public-key-등록\">Gitbub에 ssh public key 등록</div></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>가지고 있는 Github의 계정마다 아래의 방법대로 반복을 하면된다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/login\">Github</a>에 로그인한다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 404px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 140%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"20200118001 1\"\n        title=\"20200118001 1\"\n        src=\"/static/5f1ae8b47355d1bfd42b6fc62663c04a/494f9/20200118001_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5f1ae8b47355d1bfd42b6fc62663c04a/5a46d/20200118001_1.png 300w,\n/static/5f1ae8b47355d1bfd42b6fc62663c04a/494f9/20200118001_1.png 404w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 404px) 100vw, 404px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>로그인 후 오른쪽 위 메뉴를 클릭하여 Settings를 선택한다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 361px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 125.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"20200118001 2\"\n        title=\"20200118001 2\"\n        src=\"/static/972df9effdb38f4428a5787581143bf6/39d76/20200118001_2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/972df9effdb38f4428a5787581143bf6/5a46d/20200118001_2.png 300w,\n/static/972df9effdb38f4428a5787581143bf6/39d76/20200118001_2.png 361w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 361px) 100vw, 361px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>SSH and GPG keys를 선택한다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 336px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 177.99999999999997%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"20200118001 3\"\n        title=\"20200118001 3\"\n        src=\"/static/14e96d3110246f8abc0807f52a9e8d3a/d99f2/20200118001_3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/14e96d3110246f8abc0807f52a9e8d3a/5a46d/20200118001_3.png 300w,\n/static/14e96d3110246f8abc0807f52a9e8d3a/d99f2/20200118001_3.png 336w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 336px) 100vw, 336px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>NeW SSH key를 선택한다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1015px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"20200118001 4\"\n        title=\"20200118001 4\"\n        src=\"/static/570ef01417381930ae558f01c6dc9b39/e088a/20200118001_4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/570ef01417381930ae558f01c6dc9b39/5a46d/20200118001_4.png 300w,\n/static/570ef01417381930ae558f01c6dc9b39/0a47e/20200118001_4.png 600w,\n/static/570ef01417381930ae558f01c6dc9b39/e088a/20200118001_4.png 1015w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1015px) 100vw, 1015px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>“Title” 과 “Key”를 입력후 “Add SSH key”버튼을 누른다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1005px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"20200118001 5\"\n        title=\"20200118001 5\"\n        src=\"/static/df5c6ae0987fd22540bf79a551fec9ba/18c13/20200118001_5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/df5c6ae0987fd22540bf79a551fec9ba/5a46d/20200118001_5.png 300w,\n/static/df5c6ae0987fd22540bf79a551fec9ba/0a47e/20200118001_5.png 600w,\n/static/df5c6ae0987fd22540bf79a551fec9ba/18c13/20200118001_5.png 1005w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1005px) 100vw, 1005px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>아래와같이 SSH key가 정상적으로 등록된다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 998px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"20200118001 6\"\n        title=\"20200118001 6\"\n        src=\"/static/62c388efa5bf7e47f272818c526b0314/350de/20200118001_6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/62c388efa5bf7e47f272818c526b0314/5a46d/20200118001_6.png 300w,\n/static/62c388efa5bf7e47f272818c526b0314/0a47e/20200118001_6.png 600w,\n/static/62c388efa5bf7e47f272818c526b0314/350de/20200118001_6.png 998w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 998px) 100vw, 998px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"div-idssh-config-파일-설정ssh-config-파일-설정div\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#div-idssh-config-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95ssh-config-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95div\" aria-label=\"div idssh config 파일 설정ssh config 파일 설정div permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a><div id=\"ssh-config-파일-설정\">ssh config 파일 설정</div></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>C:\\Users\\사용자계정.ssh폴더에 config 파일을 편집기로 연다.(파일이 존재하지 않으면 새로 만들어준다.)</li>\n<li>config 파일을 작성한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">    Host <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span>                   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ssh 명령어에서 사용할 단어\"</span>\n    HostName github.com         <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"github 도메인\"</span>\n    User github_id              <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"github 사용자 아이디\"</span>\n    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa  <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"생성된 개인키 경로\"</span>\n\n    또는\n\n    Host <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span>                   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ssh 명령어에서 사용할 단어\"</span>\n    User github_id              <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"github 사용자 아이디\"</span>\n    Hostname ssh.github.com     <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"github 도메인\"</span>\n    PreferredAuthentications publickey  <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> 인증키\n    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"생성된 개인키 경로\"</span>\n    Port <span class=\"token number\">443</span>                    <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> 포트</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">    <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> -T git@test\n    Hi <span class=\"token string\">\"your User\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span> You've successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"div-idssh-명령어-모음ssh-명령어-모음div\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#div-idssh-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%EC%96%B4-%EB%AA%A8%EC%9D%8Cssh-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%EC%96%B4-%EB%AA%A8%EC%9D%8Cdiv\" aria-label=\"div idssh 명령어 모음ssh 명령어 모음div permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a><div id=\"ssh-명령어-모음\">ssh 명령어 모음</div></h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">eval</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>ssh-agent -s<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>  <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> ssh-agent background실행\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> ssh-add ~/.ssh/id_rsa <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> 개인키 추가\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> ssh-add -l            <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> 추가 조회\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> -T git@<span class=\"token string\">\"config파일의 Host\"</span>    <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> 접속 테스트</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"div-idssh-key-설정중-발생한-오류ssh-key-설정중-발생한-오류div\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#div-idssh-key-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%EC%A4%91-%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D%ED%95%9C-%EC%98%A4%EB%A5%98ssh-key-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%EC%A4%91-%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D%ED%95%9C-%EC%98%A4%EB%A5%98div\" aria-label=\"div idssh key 설정중 발생한 오류ssh key 설정중 발생한 오류div permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a><div id=\"ssh-key-설정중-발생한-오류\">ssh key 설정중 발생한 오류</div></h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>$ <span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> -T test@github.com <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> 잘못되었음\ntest@github.com: Permission denied <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>publickey<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>.</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>명령어 잘못 입력함.<br>\nssh -T git@test => 이렇게 되어야함.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>$ <span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> -T git_id@git_id.github.com <span class=\"token operator\">></span> 잘못되었음\nssh: connect to <span class=\"token function\">host</span> git_id.github.com port <span class=\"token number\">22</span>: Connection timed out</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>명령어 잘못 입력함.<br>\nssh -T git@test => 이렇게 되어야함.</p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"github 멀티계정 변경하기 - ssh key","date":"November 04, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/git/github-멀티계정-변경하기--